{
  "text": "Why did they want larger and stronger uh organisms? The ones of Yahweh were attempting to create an understanding of the law of one by creating mind of body complexes capable of grasping the law of one. The experiment was a decided failure from the view of the desired distortions due to the fact that rather than assimilating the law of one, it was a great temptation to consider the so-called social complex or subcomplex as elite or different and better than others. This one of the techniques of service to self.",
